                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Montreal Canada E</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>April 18<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 18<add>?</add>7</date>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">The <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dr Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It should not have troubled<lb/> you just now when I know your<lb/>\n                time must be occupied in your<lb/> great field of labour, but it<lb/> being a matter\n                concerning our<lb/> holy Religion, I trust you will<lb/> lend me a helping\n                hand.<lb/> A man by the name of <persName>Henry<lb/> Silverstone</persName> has\n                applied to me<lb/> to give him <add>חופה וקידושין</add> on my<lb/> objecting to\n                grant his request,<lb/> on the grounds of having heard<lb/> that he had a Wife in\n                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,<lb/> he then produced me a letter<lb/> from\n                a <persName>Michael Eakerman</persName> his</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33f4m77w/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
